    },
    {
      "id": "637c12c96eb40600002441dd",
      "text": "  \t修理・改造で困るのは保証の問題",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1669075658,
      "updated": 1669075668
    },
    {
      "id": "637c12d46eb40600002441de",
      "text": "  \t利用者が[As your own risk]で破壊する分には構わない",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
